import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { WebserviceService } from '../service/webservice.service'; @Component({ selector: 'auto', templateUrl: './auto.component.html', styleUrls: ['./auto.component.css'] }) export class AutoComponent implements OnInit{ private url: string = 'http://localhost:8888/'; data: any; constructor(public webserviceService: WebserviceService) { } async ngOnInit(){ await this.webserviceService.getCarsSql('getCars'); console.log(this.webserviceService.myCars); } }
